{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act25side", "eventName": "孤星", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CW-9", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "恩怨糾葛", "storyInfo": "斐爾迪南展露真心。帕爾維斯展露瘋狂。千夫所指之下，斐爾迪南巋然不動。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope02_intro", "key": "$newhope02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經，對於這片大地，抬頭仰望沒有意義。"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡不值得被觀察，那裡不值得被探索，那裡是湎於幻想之人的歸宿。"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，現在，每個人都在抬頭仰望，抬頭仰望那道連接天與地的光束。"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仰望著從來便觸不可及的天空。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g18_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "y": 100.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星辰中，在光流中顯得如此渺小的人造物，正醞釀著屬於這個時代的，人類的野心。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g3_rhinelab_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰，克麗斯騰......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你果然早就做好了計劃，國防部之前所有的行動都只是在做無用功。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈！這到底是什麼原理？這種高能約束場的效率與穩定性......我從沒聽說過。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得你在剛加入萊茵的時候，向我吹噓過，你是高能物理領域最好的科學家。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......之一。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天哪。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭，你該慶幸，你所涉獵的學術領域裡沒有一位克麗斯騰這樣的人物。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很不公平。而她......甚至不屑於發表這些成果。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聚焦發生器正在蓄能。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照軍方的“地平弧光計劃”，等充能階段結束，這些能量將會聚焦並二度激發，在大範圍內進行強力打擊。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。還要充多久？", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰把計劃書變成了廢紙......我只能說，不會太久。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我們停下它的最後機會。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是停下她的最後機會。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南，你還在發什麼愣，我們的時間不多。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭，看看那邊的密度儀。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指針好像很不穩定。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是指針，搖擺是高能約束場的正常現象。我說的是......讀數單位。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以猜猜，這個單位，是我實驗室裡儀錶的多少倍。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它剛才吸收的能量，足足能夠維持整個哥倫比亞所有移動城市至少半年的消耗。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它甚至依然沒有停下的跡象。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們，現在就在承載了如此龐大能量的實驗室中央。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使娜斯提天縱之才，她也製造不出能儲存超出現有認知水準的能量的容器。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是——", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論它最終將能量聚焦向什麼方向，只要二度激發開始，這座實驗室就一定無法倖免於難。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的目標從未變過。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她的目標真的是天空，如果天空必須要用這個等級的能量才能挑戰......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天上究竟有什麼？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不關心。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只知道，這是一場冒進而無謀的實驗。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且註定墜落。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭，你現在完全可以打道回府，找個視野開闊的山坡，一邊喝酒，一邊欣賞一朵或許將永載哥倫比亞史冊的煙火。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種情況不會發生。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢？你不會這麼冒險。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來是我的老朋友來了，他們的速度比我想的要快。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對，我可不打算冒險，技術手冊上記錄了逃生艙段的位置，我知道在哪。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒興趣去見開除我的那個人，你也用不上我幫忙。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記錄眼下這種高能物理現象的機會很少，我不會錯過這樣的機會。也許下個季度你能在學報上看到我的新論文。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我保證，那一定會是劃時代的一篇。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰把她所有的智慧都綁在了個人的偏執上，我和她不一樣。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會同意......她把這些足以改變整個泰拉學界的知識就此葬送。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忙你的去吧，塞雷婭，我們的時間都不多。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保重。", "name": "塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南。", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見，上校。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能活下來，我不意外，但如果我是你，我會假裝自己已經死了。", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開這裡，跑去維多利亞或者萊塔尼亞，憑你的本事，謀一份教職總是可以的。", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不像是你會說出的話，上校。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再說一遍，斐爾迪南，已經結束了。", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和副總統已經談過了，國防部輸得很徹底。", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於這件事還能不能被挽回，我的命最終會交到誰的手上，我其實已經沒那麼關心了。", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們留些體面吧，斐爾迪南，滾開，我可以省下一支弩箭留給自己。", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你在說什麼？抱歉，我剛剛沒注意聽。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，你擋住射線儀的螢幕了。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座能量井，比我想像的要深得多......", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕軍方根本沒有完全掌握它的結構。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡......是傳導物質反應最強的地方。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_prison_commandroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_labamb", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默，你怎麼在這裡？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕爾維斯......老師......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默......這間實驗室的位置應該是保密的，你怎麼找到這裡來的？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默努力睜大眼睛，辨別著房間裡的東西。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "房間的角落裡，儀器正發出呼吸一般的嗡鳴，一個透明的罐體中，傳導物質正在其中浮沉。另一邊，放著幾本封皮漆黑的書籍。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "似乎感受到赫默的存在，傳導物質稍稍活躍了些。強烈的暈眩感讓赫默皺緊了眉頭，搖晃了幾下。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對了，你也有傳導物質......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，這些活性傾向......你給自己注射了傳導物質？倒也不意外。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是偶爾會有不適感？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是正常反應，我身體裡也有這些東西，對於你們年輕人應該還好，我這樣上了年紀的人，確實會感覺有點吃不消。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，只有這樣才能更好地控制反應進程。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，等到實驗結束，這批傳導物質的跨距離糾纏性質會喪失，不會影響到注射者未來的健康狀況。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實驗？您在這裡做實驗？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默，你的手受傷了？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "影響活動嗎？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我也就不多問了，現在是最關鍵的時刻。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能找到這裡，也許真的能幫上我的忙。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才我還在念叨，如果你在的話，資料處理方面我能輕鬆不少。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最近......不，算了。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您到底在做什麼實驗？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真正投入精力的研究方向始終只有一個。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嵌合實驗。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，這是嵌合實驗的最後一個課題。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，這裡......", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，這些文獻是什麼？這上面的文字給人的感覺......", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很“邪惡”，對吧？這是薩卡茲的古籍，記錄了某個分支種族的“歷史”。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個分支的薩卡茲不僅擁有長久的生命，還能跨越肉體的束縛，以一種純精神態在世間存在。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們被稱為“死魂靈”。這個發音非常晦澀，但姑且能找到一些維多利亞語的記錄。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默，你有沒有想過，靈魂層面上的嵌合會產生什麼影響？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靈魂的嵌合？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種“死魂靈”......古老源石技藝和薩卡茲巫術裡所謂的“靈魂”，有可能透過後天手段產生嗎？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您——", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在試圖創造一種人造意識？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直是我最好的學生。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這項工作我已經進行了數十年，進展一直很有限，直到斐爾迪南告訴我，他和多蘿西共同製造了這種特別的“傳導物質”。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒法想像當時我有多興奮，赫默！", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我完全可以肯定，“傳導物質”的性質......足夠成為人造意識誕生的土壤。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，在這片大地上，無論多精密的實驗室，擾動卻始終存在。這些擾動困擾了我很久......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有很多種可能，也許是激發傳導物質的能量不夠大，也許是實驗室的密閉等級還不夠，源石干擾了意識的產生與聚合。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，不再重要了。赫默，今天一切的困惑都會獲得解答。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這會是我最後的研究。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最為理想的實驗環境即將形成。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕爾維斯老師......您負責用傳導物質解決“弧光一號”的操縱精度問題，您這裡......是傳導物質新的中樞。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰想做些自以為冒險的事，她認為她的工作很有意義......我不願評判同行的成果，但說實話，我們這些研究者懦弱得太久了。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平庸、無聊、保守、瞻前顧後......赫默，我們這些擁有知識、擁有能力的人，所要做的從來不只是“探索”或“進步”。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們背負科學，我們被它命令，供它驅策，它要求我們承擔起強大的靈魂才能承擔的職責。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——開創一個新的時代。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“開創一個新的時代”？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默......你有資格與我一起見證這真正偉大成果的誕生。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快了，很快了......平庸的歲月將要結束，科學的神祇必須歸位。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您在顫抖，老師。我很少見您這副樣子。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？也許是傳導物質的反應太強烈了，也許是我真的上了年紀。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默，我相信你能感同身受。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我能。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，您真的很期待這一刻。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，老師，我必須向您坦白，我會摧毀傳導物質的中樞。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼，赫默？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，我會停下這裡正在發生的一切。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論是總轄的計劃，還是您的野心，都必須要被重新審視。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這正是我來到這裡的目的。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個孩子動搖了你對於科學的忠誠，但我始終相信，你有一個研究者的品質。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我從沒有真正地責怪你。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，這次，不管你是不是在開一個荒唐的玩笑，我都不能容忍。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要你向我道歉，赫默。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會收回我說的任何一句話，老師。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是當年，還是現在，我都不認為我做錯了什麼。你們真正想要的，是肆意妄為的權力。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可笑。赫默，你大錯特錯。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，你可以說，我要的是肆意妄為的權力，那是因為我知道，哪些研究是重要的，哪些研究能開創未來。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想和我說那套科學屬於大眾的陳腔濫調？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不！", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須告訴你，赫默，科學屬於超人。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庸眾可以去選擇政客，庸眾可以去崇拜領袖......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但唯有科學，他們不配染指。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您呢，老師？您是自己希望的那種，“超人”嗎？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我已經沒有機會了。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果我創造出的這種意識足夠理性，足夠宏偉，它就能夠——", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它不能，老師。", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您連人都不相信，您憑什麼認為一個初生的意識，就能超越這片大地上的一切呢？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不明白，赫默。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您把全部的心血投入在嵌合實驗這個項目上，一次次期待以生物工程的方式創造強大的造物，是不是正因為......", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您無法回避自己的羸弱呢？", "name": "赫默"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......！", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......赫默，你不能這麼揣測我。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我......擺脫平庸的，最後的希望。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g3_rhinelab_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我沒有想到，在這裡能看到你們。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "防衛科曾經的同僚們。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，塞雷婭主任，“曾經的同僚”。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在是總轄構件科雇員。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“總轄構件科”。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不能通過這裡。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.04, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.01, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing5", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.04, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing3", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們做得比上次要好。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們知道克麗斯騰想做什麼，這只會——", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道，我也並不在乎。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我在萊茵的員工編號，塞雷婭。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "011，那時候雅拉還沒來，是我和克麗斯騰一起面試的你，詹姆。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時，我也收到了其他公司的邀請，沃爾沃特科欽斯基還有沙灘傘，但我沒有一秒考慮過它們。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我始終相信著你們，塞雷婭，還有克麗斯騰。因為我相信你們與他們不同。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這只是你的自我感動，詹姆，這裡很快就會墜毀，我建議你們馬上乘坐逃生艙段離開。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會等到墜毀那一刻。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，在此之前，想看見些特別的景色嗎，塞雷婭？", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提對我們形容過這一幕......", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭察覺到，整個走廊正在偏移。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是——", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#3$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 7.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g4_rhinelab_corridor_rised", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 7.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我從沒在這個高度俯瞰過大地。", "name": "總轄構件科雇員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——聚焦發生器已經開始姿態調整。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒時間了，讓開！", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#11$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g4_rhinelab_corridor_rised", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，怎麼回事？這東西在轉？", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜，這是技術手冊上說的“姿態調整”，是二次激發的前置步驟。", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，需要我扶您一把嗎？", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......走廊裡的這些門怎麼關上了？斐爾迪南呢？", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他趁剛剛的機會——", "name": "哥倫比亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我追上他！", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g5_rhinelab_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了走廊的隔斷門，這裡就沒有別的自衛系統了嗎？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是我的話，一定在這裡塞滿動力甲。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不許動，斐爾迪南。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逮到你了。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不想讓你們繼續打擾我，上校，在這裡的每一分鐘都很寶貴。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而與你們打交道會浪費掉我所有的精力。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原本以為我們是同類，斐爾迪南，我們是清醒的理性主義者，會權衡利弊後再做決定。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我看錯你了。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟我們走。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "射線激發的讀數是1.22，這裡應該需要引入一個常數，來重整化整個公式......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼？", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#3$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，我在嘲笑你，布萊克。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "38_i11", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 0.85, "yScaleTo": 0.85, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在嘲笑你，多可悲，權力、勳章、你在國防部的地位......你的眼睛永遠無法從那些東西上移開。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我們正站在幾乎沒有人觸及過的高度，被科學的奇蹟環繞，幾乎隨手就能從儀器中摘出一條新的公式。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以看到，在這裡，你所執著的那些榮譽是多麼渺小。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你的萊茵生命呢，斐爾迪南？", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是你緊緊盯著的東西嗎？", "name": "布萊克"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要糾正你一點，我盯著的是萊茵生命所代表的東西。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命是我的手段，我的階梯，我的臂膀。但不是目的。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕您忘了，我可以自豪地宣稱，我是這片大地......不，現在是大地與天空，最優秀的高能物理學家之一。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我盯著的，從來只有科學本身。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰，克麗斯騰......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她創造了這些，她浪費了這些，她是個奢侈的天才。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我如此地嫉妒——", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我也不得不承認，我如此地享受。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，現在我的每一分每一秒都如此重要，沒有一點點時間可以浪費在你身上。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以命令你，斐爾迪南，別忘了你該聽命於誰，別忘了是誰給了你一次新的機會！", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#7$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校，你知道怎麼阻止一個好奇的科學家嗎？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#7$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滿足他，或者，殺死他。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_890_1#2$1"}, {"id": 454, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#4$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解決掉，別浪費時間。", "name": "布萊克"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_899_1#1$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一件事，我需要提醒你們，士兵。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座聚焦發生器會在二次激發後墜毀，連帶著我們所有人。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許這些資料對你們沒意義，但是你們的命......我相信，很重要。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們想知道逃生艙段在哪就不要那麼急著動手。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 471, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_890_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你，布萊克，留好你的弩箭吧......射向你自己，或者你的頂頭上司什麼的，我無所謂。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 473, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，不要打壞我的儀器。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 479, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}